this version sounds like a late 1970s fusion version with fender Rhodes and guitar through distortion (ritenouer? scofield?). more than competent, but not coltrane.

Last FM must pull/play different tracks with the same title.  What I got was a very recent cover of Coltrane's "Moment's Notice," but absolutely not the original from Blue Trane.  Coltrane is not playing on this track--in fact, I don't think there is even a sax.  Keyboard is playing all the sax lines.  Not horrible, but not Coltrane as labled.
Not Coltrane?! This is Blue Train! Are you insane?!
